# Pet Adoption Platform

## Project Overview
The Pet Adoption Platform is a Spring Boot-based web application that allows users to adopt pets and view available pets for adoption. It supports functionalities like user registration, pet adoption, and viewing pet profiles.

## Features
- **User Registration**: Users can create an account.
- **Pet Adoption**: Users can view available pets and adopt them.
- **Pet Profiles**: Each pet has a profile with details like name, type, and adoption status.

## Technology Stack
- **Backend**: Spring Boot (Java 11)
- **Database**: H2 Database (in-memory for development/testing)
- **Testing**: JUnit, Mockito for unit testing
- **Other**: Maven for dependency management

## Setup Instructions
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/pet-adoption-platform.git
mvn install
mvn spring-boot:run
mvn test

